<div class="row">
  <div id="banner-container" class="hero-banner">
    <div class=" large-12 columns">
      <h1>Build Love<br/>Where it's needed most</h1>
      <%= link_to "Create Your Registry", new_registry_path, :id => "cta-button", :class => "button large" %>
    </div>
    <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="row heartfully-summary">
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h2>Heartful.ly</h2>
    <p>creates charitable wedding registries that can share your happily ever after with the world. We offer engaged couples a platform to register for small scale, high impact infrastructure and development projects around the world.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="large-6 columns small-only-text-center medium-only-text-center large-only-text-right xlarge-only-text-right">
    <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/119511358" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="row heartfully-how-it-works">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns"><h2><span class="line-center">How It Works</span></h2></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-3 columns">
      <h2>Explore</h2>
      <div class="row"><%= image_tag "explore_icon.png", alt: "Exlpore Icon" %></div>
      <p>Whether you're passionate about alternative energy, healthy moms and babies or clean drinking water, we will help you find a registry that reflects your values.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-3 columns">
      <h2>Confirm</h2>
      <div class="row"><%= image_tag "confirm_icon.png", alt: "Exlpore Icon" %></div>
      <p>Found "the one?" Let us know the project you'd like to support and we'll set up your registry webpage. We will transform the project into individual gifts like pallets of bricks and buckets of paint. We'll also add an overview of the project to your page.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-3 columns">
      <h2>Customize</h2>
      <div class="row"><%= image_tag "customize_icon.png", alt: "Exlpore Icon" %></div>
      <p>We turn the resigns over to you to write a note to your guests, add photos, and even record a video message. When you're ready, share yout one-of-a-kind wedding registry with your guests using our straight forward web tools.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-3 columns">
      <h2>Give</h2>
      <div class="row"><%= image_tag "build_icon.png", alt: "Exlpore Icon" %></div>
      <p>On your wedding day, we transfer your guests' donations to the organization implementing the project. You will receive multimedia updates as the work progresses and upon completion of any infrastructure project, a plague will be hung in your name on site.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

